{"tid":1768020,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"知識係最好口既防蟲劑","createTime":"2019-12-03T18:24:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-03T18:30:04.000Z","uid":137017,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"e8611832c870fdea91b0763c636c61757b626ac0","tid":1768020,"uid":137017,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-03T18:24:42.000Z","msg":"之前細佬借Ac招義補，我當時係唔明佢諗緊咩，因為一個人根本幫唔到幾多個都唔知佢做乜，剛剛宵夜忍唔住問佢<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />弟<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：多D人可以接受高等教育世界都好D，令佢哋做個有思考同良知既人，幫到幾多幫幾多<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：咁好多人或者高官都有讀書，都唔見得好有良知同思考能力<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：呢個係概率問題姐，同埋政府高官好多都好醒，嚴格來講佢哋係自私扮傻<br />\n         調返轉啦，你想多啲人入大學定多啲人入毅進？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有幾秒覺得我細佬幾型<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9ccb538d42ba75fcffae879467a8b479dfd92d3","tid":1768020,"uid":171561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-03T18:29:08.000Z","msg":"好型<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9442fc5f5928bf37958da2a9a549d80c2144499","tid":1768020,"uid":335391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-03T18:30:04.000Z","msg":"好兄弟，通常第二句我哋就開拖。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}